00:04:42.740 --> 00:04:46.700
How to control the ball in the air ?

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:51.800
A good chest control offers to physical strickers the chance to be deadly in the goal area

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:57.640
with some good players you can also make a  chest control and  a dribbling skill

00:04:58.060 --> 00:05:02.580
to make a short chest control be careful to be at the right distance from the ball

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:05.280
and to make a chest control with a quick second touch

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:09.180
be at the right distance and push quickly the R3 Button while the ball is still in the air

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:13.300
timing must be perfect or else you will loose the ball

00:05:17.140 --> 00:05:18.960
To control the ball while your player is still running

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:20.840
just move your player toward the ball and if

00:05:21.100 --> 00:05:25.000
his dribbling stat is good, he will push his leg forward to catch it

00:05:25.180 --> 00:05:28.520
How to fake a ball control ?

00:05:30.300 --> 00:05:35.640
Against aggressive players you can fake your ball control

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:40.560
to do so just hold the right stick in a direction before receiving the ball

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:45.760
then activate your dribbling control just after with the left stick (hold) by choising a direction

00:05:46.420 --> 00:05:49.980
as you can see the right stick is for the ball direction

00:05:50.140 --> 00:05:53.120
and the left stick is for the body direction

00:05:53.320 --> 00:05:57.400
you can also let the ball go through your legs by holding L1 and R1 buttons

00:05:57.620 --> 00:06:01.040
a very effective tips against opponents rushing for the ball

