The Super Cancel move is a simple (and useful) Pro Evolution Soccer Tips

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:24.300
by holding R1 and R2 buttons, you have a full control of your player

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:28.660
in front of the attack, it allows you to anticipate a pass and beat your opponent

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:32.840
in defense you can anticipate for a forward pass

00:06:33.100 --> 00:06:36.320
and during the match, the Super Cancel tips allows you to let the ball go out the field

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:39.460
or to have a second chance after a poor pass

